quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  28,51,Ndithudi tatumiza mawu athu motsatana kwa iwo kuti akhoze kuchenjezedwa
  28,52,"Iwo amene kale tidawapatsa Buku lino lisadadze, amakhulupirira mwa ilo"
  28,53,"Pamene limalakatulidwa kwa iwo, amati iwowo “Ife tili kulikhulupirira Bukuli chifukwa ndi choonadi chochokera kwa Ambuye wathu. Ife tidadzipereka kwathunthu kalekale mawu awa asadadze.”"
  28,54,Anthu awa mphotho yawo idzaperekedwa kwa iwo kawiri chifukwa iwo adapirira ndipo amagonjetsa choipa pochita chabwino ndi kumapereka gawo la chaulere pa katundu amene tidawapatsa
  28,55,"Ndipo iwo akamva mawu oipa, salabadira zonenazo koma amati, “Ife tili ndi ntchito zathu ndipo nanunso muli ndi ntchito zanu. Mtendere ukhale kwa inu. Ife sitifuna kugwirizana ndi anthu osadziwa.”"
  28,56,Iwe siungamutsogolere aliyense amene umufuna. Ndi Mulungu yekha amene amatsogolera aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Iye amadziwa bwino anthu amene ali oyenera
  28,57,"Iwo amati, “Ngati ife titsatira chilangizo chako, ife tikuopakulandidwadzikolathu.”KodiIfesitidawakhazikire malo otetezedwa kumene zipatso za mtundu uliwonse zimaperekedwa ngati chakudya kuchokera kwa Ife? Ndithudi ambiri a iwo ndi anthu osadziwa"
  28,58,Kodi ndi mizinda ingati imene tidaononga imene idali kunyada chifukwa cha chuma chake? Kotero zimenezi ndizo nyumba zawo zimene sadakhalitsemo ndipo tsopano eni ake ndife
  28,59,"Ndipo Ambuye wako sadaononge mizinda mpaka pamene Iye adadzutsa kuchokera mu iyo, Mtumwi amene amalalikira za chivumbulutso chathu ndipo Ife sitidzaononga mzinda pokhapokha anthu okhala mmenemo ali olakwa"
  28,60,Zinthu zimene mwapatsidwa si zina koma chakudya ndiponso chionetsero chopanda pake cha m’moyo uno. Koma chimene chili ndi Mulungu ndicho chabwino ndiponso chokhalitsa. Kodi simungathe kuzindikira
  28,61,Kodi anthu awiriwa ndi ofanana? Iye amene tamulonjeza lonjezo labwino ndipo adzalikwaniritsa ndi iye amene tamupatsa zokoma zambiri za m’moyo uno koma pa tsiku lachiweruzo adzakhala m’gulu la iwo olangidwa
  28,62,"Pa tsiku limeneli Mulungu adzawaitana ndipo adzati, “Kodi aja munkati ndi anzanga ali kuti?”"
  28,63,"Iwo amene adzapezeka ndi mlandu wotere adzati, “Awa ndiwo anthu amene ife tidawasocheretsa. Ife tidawasocheretsa chifukwa nafenso tidali osochera. Ife tsopano tadzipatula (kuchoka mwa iwo) ndi kudza kwa inu. Si ndife amene iwo anali kupembedza.”"
  28,64,"Ndipo kudzanenedwa kwa iwo kuti, “Itanani anzanu kuti akuthandizeni.” Iwo adzawaitana koma iwo sadzawamva ayi. Ndipo iwo adzalawa chilango chowawa. Iwo adzafunitsitsa akadatsogozedwa bwino"
  28,65,"Tsiku limene Mulungu adzawaitana nati, “Kodi inu mudanena zotani kwa Mtumwi?”"
  28,66,"Zodandaula zawo sizidzamveka ayi, kotero sadzatha kufunsana wina ndi mnzake"
  28,67,"Akakhala iye amene alapa zoipa zake nakhulupirira ndipo achita ntchito zabwino, mwina akhoza kudzakhala pakati pa anthu opambana"
  28,68,Ndipo Ambuye wako amalenga ndi kusankha aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Kusankha si kwawo ayi. Ulemerero ukhale kwa Mulungu ndipo Iye atalikirane ndi zimene amamufanizira nazo
  28,69,Ambuye wako amadziwa zonse zimene amazibisa m’mitima mwawo ndiponso zimene amaziulula
  28,70,Iye ndi Mulungu ndipo palibenso mulungu wina koma Iye yekha. Kuyamikidwa konse ndi kwake m’moyo uno ndiponso m’moyo umene uli nkudza. Ndipo chake ndi chiweruzo ndipo kwa Iye mudzabwerera
  28,71,"Nena, “Ndiuzeni! Ngati Mulungu atapanga usiku kuti usache mpaka pa tsiku louka kwa akufa, kodi ndi mulungu uti kupatula Mulungu weniweni amene akhoza kukupatsani usana? Kodi simukumva?”"
  28,72,"Nena, “Ndiuzeni! Ngati Mulungu atapanga usana kuti kusade mpaka pa tsiku louka kwa akufa, kodi ndi mulungu uti kupatula Mulungu weniweni amene akhoza kukupatsani usiku umene inu mumapumulamo? Kodi inu simukuona?”"
  28,73,Mwachifundo chake wakupatsani usiku ndi usana kuti muzipezamo mpumulo ndi kufunafuna chisomo chake ndi kuti muzithokoza
  28,74,"Ndipo pa tsiku limene adzawaitana iwo nati, “Kodi ali kuti iwo amene mumaganiza kuti ndi anzanga?”"
  28,75,"Ndipo nthawi yomweyo tidzaitana mboni kuchokera ku mtundu uliwonse ndipo tidzati, “Bweretsani umboni wanu.” Nthawi imeneyo adzadziwa kuti mwini wake choonadi ndi Mulungu ndipo zonse zimene amapeka zidzawathawira"